Day 54: Kubernetes Shared Volumes

Date: October 24, 2025
Overview
Implemented shared volumes between containers in a pod.
Key Concepts Learned

EmptyDir volumes
Volume sharing
Inter-container communication
Data persistence within pods

Commands Used
yamlvolumes:
- name: shared-data
  emptyDir: {}
volumeMounts:
- name: shared-data
  mountPath: /data
Challenges Faced
Understanding volume lifecycle and when data persists vs gets deleted.
